    edu.rit.pj2.vbl
    Package edu.rit.pj2.vbl contains general-purpose reduction variable classes that implement interface Vbl.

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DoubleHistogramVbl
      Class DoubleHistogramVbl is the abstract base class for a histogram that categorizes values of type double into bins and counts the number of occurrences in each bin.
      class  FloatHistogramVbl
      Class FloatHistogramVbl is the abstract base class for a histogram that categorizes values of type float into bins and counts the number of occurrences in each bin.
      class  IntHistogramVbl
      Class IntHistogramVbl is the abstract base class for a histogram that categorizes values of type int into bins and counts the number of occurrences in each bin.
      class  LongHistogramVbl
      Class LongHistogramVbl is the abstract base class for a histogram that categorizes values of type long into bins and counts the number of occurrences in each bin.
      class  ObjectHistogramVbl<T>
      Class ObjectHistogramVbl is the abstract base class for a histogram that categorizes values of an object type into bins and counts the number of occurrences in each bin.
